# {{.Name}} ({{.Type}})

{{ .Description | trimspace }}

The `search` is a raw FHIR query string. The provider appends `_summary=count` and returns the server's `Bundle.total`. To preview how many resources a `medplum_fhir_data_migration` still has to process, include the same `_tag:not=<marker_system>/<name>|<hash>` filter the migration uses — the count then converges to zero as the migration completes.

